  7,58,"The vegetation of a good land comes forth (easily) by the Permission of its Lord; and that which is bad, brings forth nothing but (a little) with difficulty. Thus do We explain variously the Ayât (proofs, evidence, verses, lessons, signs, revelations, etc.) for a people who give thanks."
  7,59,"Indeed, We sent Nûh (Noah) to his people and he said: "
  7,60,"The leaders of his people said: "